column5: Is there one web site that lists most of the resorts on the west portion of Lac Suel? Maybe a general tourist site or association of lodge owners. Would like to see what the options or choices are. thanks!
http://www.ontariossunsetcountry.ca/...tbid=7&code=19 and scroll down. Should give you a listing of alot of the resorts around the western side.
Thanks 2 DOGS, exactly what I was looking for! Gotta love WC folks.
